{"tid":1245931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係私院護士 想澄清","createTime":"2019-06-20T13:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:56:26.000Z","uid":71915,"like":12,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef618fe3ed67062b05f5d1f756d1eb7878d1571","tid":1245931,"uid":71915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"我唔係港安醫院嘅護士<br />\n<br />\n我都唔支持港安醫院報警<br />\n<br />\n如果港安醫院真係有報警我都會大大力咁屌佢<br />\n<br />\nOn9醫院，垃圾醫生護士<br />\n<br />\n我成個post嘅重點係教人點樣去私院接受治癒<br />\n<br />\n大家點諗我唔在乎<br />\n<br />\n我講多最後一次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實你講你點受傷我哋就信<br />\n<br />\n你講你打war game受槍傷<br />\n<br />\n你講你碌落樓梯成身瘀曬<br />\n<br />\n你講你俾啲不明液體濺咗入眼睛<br />\n<br />\n私家醫院絕對係會醫你並且絕對唔會報警</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要屌就屌<br />\n<br />\n但紅字要切記！"},{"pid":"60491ececfe4a0dfd8e6230711cdfca7c4743868","tid":1245931,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5ea9de0a070c9dc76d5d1dd3ddaca71db3c217a","tid":1245931,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60491ececfe4a0dfd8e6230711cdfca7c4743868","tid":1245931,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"雙目失明"},{"pid":"8ea7f7a2ff3b61e929c2df87fdabeedb42586293","tid":1245931,"uid":8500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"bfa219529b6852a5ef8e5b86a189f9c09d7893c5","tid":1245931,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"90後的你人工有幾多？<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/oQNObV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/oQNObV</a><br />\n#24 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nHD 出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n